properties.areaDesc: Ventura County Mountains; Los Angeles County Mountains excluding the Santa Monica Range
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 2 at 6:23AM PST until January 2 at 3:00PM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...North to northeast winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts to 50
mph.

* WHERE...Ventura County Mountains and Los Angeles County
Mountains excluding the Santa Monica Range.

* WHEN...Until 3 PM PST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and
make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Winds will be northerly Wednesday night,
then become northeasterly Thursday morning.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 PM PST THIS AFTERNOON... ...HIGH WIND WARNING IS CANCELLED
